  "title": "CSO- Housekeeping Supervisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>CSO- Housekeeping Supervisor</strong></p>\n<p>If you are a dynamic and motivated person who has strong interpersonal skills and more importantly, believe that YOU CAN MAKE A DIFFERENCE to the company, we would like to hear from you.</p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Supervise and coordinate the daily cleaning operations across cinema halls, lobbies, restrooms and other areas</li>\n  <li>Prepare monthly cleaners’ work schedule</li>\n  <li>Assign tasks, monitor performance and ensure high cleanliness standards are consistently met</li>\n  <li>Conduct regular inspections and ensure health &amp; safety compliance</li>\n  <li>Train and guide cleaning staff on proper procedures and use of equipment</li>\n  <li>Handle stock and supply levels e.g. cleaning products, toilet paper etc</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Previous experiences in cleaning supervision in cinema, hotel, commercial cleaning or similar preferred</li>\n  <li>Strong leadership and communication skills</li>\n  <li>Familiar with health and safety standards and cleaning protocols</li>\n  <li>Able to always hands-on and demonstrate team-oriented approach</li>\n  <li>Positive attitude and good team spirit</li>\n  <li>Able to work on rotating shifts and on a 5 days week basis inclusive of weekends and public holidays</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Basic + Allowances + Medical benefits + FREE movies!</li>\n  <li>Attractive bonuses</li>\n  <li>Career advancementopportunities</li>\n  <li>FUN and LIVELY workingenvironment</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested candidates please e-mail your cover letter and detailed resume with Passport Size Photograph and Indication</p>\n<p>of Expected Salary &amp; Date of Availability to:</p>\n<p><strong>The Recruitment Officer</strong></p>\n<p>Re: Application for the post of Head Chef Recruitment</p>\n<p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:recruitment@shaw.com.sg\">recruitment@shaw.com.sg</a></p>\n<p>(Only shortlisted candidates will be notified)</p>",
